      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUCY VALENTINE (2) was in the minor money with a sharp 19.71, finishing third in a Free For All at Gunnedah last start. Hard to top on the time from last start. RED ROCK RATTLER (1) started big odds over 318m at this track (18.54) in Grade 4/5 but ran very well to fill a minor placing. Was a winner the start prior in easier at this track. Can measure up. ROSACKY RAYO (7) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 18.33 beating Faith Keeping. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from six starts. Leading chance again. KIANDO HUNT (3) deserves plenty of thought over this distance.",
